title: Solar Storm Forces Changes On Space Station - Real Life Communications: #space

author: Scott Manley
description:
Last night we had amazing northern lights across the USA, but, this was because of a solar storm which is so intense that Blue Origin have postponed their planned launch attempt of the ESCAPADE spacecraft on New Glenn. 
So, what's the deal with solar activity, why would Blue Origin be worried?
